OL,3,CMillion-year-old stone tools found in
OL,4,CUkraine belonged to ancient humans
OL,6,FStone tools unearthed in a quarry in
OL,7,Fbelonged to ancient humans who used
OL,8,Fthem more than a million years ago,
OL,9,Faccording to new research.JThe
OL,10,Fartefacts - which have been dated at
OL,11,F1.4 million-years-old - reveal the
OL,12,Fearliest known presence of hominins in
OL,13,FEurope, said Roman Garba, an
OL,14,Farchaeologist at the Czech Academy of
OL,15,FSciences in Prague.
