OL,6,FArchaeologists have recovered 90,000
OL,7,Fstone tools from the site, but said no
OL,8,Fhuman fossils have been found. The
OL,9,Fexposed conditions and acidic soil
OL,10,Fmake it harder for fossils to be
OL,11,Fpreserved, Mr Garba said.
