OL,6,FTo determine the ages of the stone
OL,7,Ftools in the lowermost archaeological
OL,8,Flayer more accurately, the team used a
OL,9,Frelatively new dating method that
OL,10,Finvolved analysing radioactive
OL,11,Fparticles inside mineral grains that
OL,12,Fwere produced by cosmic rays - charged
OL,13,Fparticles that travel through space
OL,14,Fand rain down on Earth.
OL,16,F"It's like a cosmic clock that
OL,17,Funleashes human history," said Mr
OL,18,FGarba, lead author of the study.
